@NODE "History" "History"
  12.History
  ~~~~~~~~~~~

  Version 1.02

  First release.

  Version 1.2

  Hand of croupier apeared under coins already placed on table, because of
  priority of bobs. Just made bob number of hand highest number.

  Added more mouse functions. Right mouse button now equals F10 ( New game)
  Press RMB and LMB simultaniously to start the croupier
  Equals pressing spacebar. Now you can play without using keyboard.

  When no coin choise is made coin is set to 1000,=.
  Now properly shown in Bet window.

  Added option to show coin in hand of croupier, so you can actualy see
  what value of coin you're betting. Press 'C' for Coin shown On/Off

  Removed programming error which caused sometimes single bets (like red or black)
  to pay 35 x instead of 1 x.

  Removed bug that 'forgot' to show toptext " press Spacebar when done"

  Added "Help" option. Help now works with 'Help' key and 'H' key.

  Removed several minor errors and added minor improvements in layout.


  Version 1.21 (24-7-'99)

  Added one more macro under shift F6 (Covers about one side of the wheel)


  Version 1.22 (25-7-'99)

  Added option 'V'. Turns off all voices exept rolling ball
  Improved help screen under 'Help' key.

  Version 1.23 (31-7-'99)

  Added save/restore option for amount of playing money
  ( For methode testing -How to beat the casino-?)

  Version 1.24 (02-8-'99)

  Added Fading in/out on playfield.(Looks cool!)
  Added Help turn off with left mouse key( Feels more natural)
  Removed a bug that never showed!
  (Could pay money when you lost.)
  Cleaned up source and lost 10 Kb.
  Fixed a bug that caused deletion of white square
  around numbers when more than 50 coins where played
  Made number of that bob 60.

  Version 1.3 (08-08-'99)

  Added a screen for a Number Database. When 'D' is pushed a screen scrolls up
  containing all numbers and shows how many times each number has been drawn.
  This data base is automaticly loaded when the game is started and also saves
  automaticly when the game is ended. So every time the game is played every
  draw is recorded.I did this because I wanted to predict the next number
  based on the fact that one number has not been drawn a lot. Since its hard
  to code and this does absolutely not work.(In one try had not seen nr36 in
  a long time so I bet nr 36!...It took 126 draws before it came....).
  I don't think I will add this feature.

  Added yet another Macro under shift F7 (Covers all numbers and pays on Zero)

  Speeded up up/down scrolling of help and dbase screen.(took far to long)

